{"id":"486de1a3603ccf08dfc75b8d0aa4079e92627138f8b54f0e5eb039addb770b72","item_id":"4f9ab4a92b:0","text":"对传入颜色的一个或多个分量进行反相。输入颜色可以使用 RGB、HSL 或 HSV 颜色模型。注意：输出是一个 RGB 颜色，并被钳制到"}
{"id":"663ea1bfffe5038f3f0cf667f14c4257eff52d77ce7f2a218f72e9286616ea39","item_id":"4f9ab4a92b:1","text":"到"}
{"id":"5b450b391a66050b7a2b33ba81cd8e5099a373831bc01c2d021ee3242f307c5a","item_id":"4f9ab4a92b:2","text":"范围。"}
{"id":"a0fbb0152c545070cb1163ff7badbf178ac79418a41c83336fd75e19844dc148","item_id":"4f9ab4a92b:5","text":"要反相的颜色。"}
{"id":"8533fc1ad96dc818bd731e6f0a322fedf20b5d47169c49e61e25fff428f871b0","item_id":"4f9ab4a92b:6","text":"Color Model"}
{"id":"53a5e0a5df3438ae514ff7a6ca80f528ea25981f13120c3b1273e29f343b28ed","item_id":"4f9ab4a92b:7","text":"inputColor 使用此颜色模型。"}
{"id":"c9eac5388f3cc6bc6e3b72266689adc0a2ba55897ed2a123c7c9f79fb6170c0e","item_id":"4f9ab4a92b:8","text":"0: RGB"}
{"id":"2802eef0cfe483a8e3e54273a9249d76f2ac4cf0be0473f0a635c1deafc5d675","item_id":"4f9ab4a92b:9","text":"1: HSL"}
{"id":"fb8ee2cc5bcca6ce1164ae418e2dd58cf05c6583d80dfae841a7af4e7b2fa954","item_id":"4f9ab4a92b:10","text":"2: HSV"}
{"id":"aa961b6b52c85867b3a6262d347e97c7da433d6f6dd3956750b659c2dd97db6f","item_id":"4f9ab4a92b:11","text":"Invert Channel 0"}
{"id":"4903e5bcb5a0c711efef8485aa1183ccb32923e089c9e343cfba61d62e9d2cc0","item_id":"4f9ab4a92b:12","text":"启用时（设为 1），第一个颜色通道会被反相。例如，如果 Color Model 设置为 RGB，则 R 通道会被反相。"}
{"id":"f0ff9e8d5b255b45cce0f9b199d86779c14c66dda5b7066dd1a41336d4aecb7e","item_id":"4f9ab4a92b:13","text":"Invert Channel 1"}
{"id":"34205b1d3219a836a9579ceb9d1ba618393d6cc455d7a713a74aa974948dc86f","item_id":"4f9ab4a92b:14","text":"启用时（设为 1），第二个颜色通道会被反相。例如，如果 Color Model 设置为 RGB，则 G 通道会被反相。"}
{"id":"ef2f73b7b020a174dce981a99fd76940c201128c9ae02ab67ac432e89cb33daf","item_id":"4f9ab4a92b:15","text":"Invert Channel 2"}
{"id":"ce4cfbf07e65ef7c6c7f6a1afe989d032c030835dc004fdad555e014fe28195a","item_id":"4f9ab4a92b:16","text":"启用时（设为 1），第三个颜色通道会被反相。例如，如果 Color Model 设置为 RGB，则 B 通道会被反相。"}
{"id": "e8756d05615a8b9aac2d138a9ae82553f3231ff237868a66679a30001b4f326b", "item_id": "4f9ab4a92b:3", "text": "Input Parameters（输入参数）"}
{"id": "35aea6f833e7d09d9722a54bdee4bc25b02fd25547d6613ee8d9457096af94fb", "item_id": "4f9ab4a92b:4", "text": "Input Color"}
{"id": "8b76e2df9050f924b018cff8809cbc580f39a71664984ae54adf99defe9eaa2e", "item_id": "4f9ab4a92b:17", "text": "Output Parameters（输出参数）"}
{"id": "d76cd2ea3537dbac1a9b90ba977fe5ad654d6f7f3c36b060963224d8b5611f99", "item_id": "4f9ab4a92b:18", "text": "resultRGB"}
{"id": "6796d2c52b4882b98311c8be5b2889976246b071d35733a80a01da19e5bcba42", "item_id": "4f9ab4a92b:19", "text": "钳制后的颜色结果。"}
{"id": "c9223602a8320733dcf0de118c9880f9df06acdfdb068bb26ba166fc96c52d6c", "item_id": "4f9ab4a92b:20", "text": "resultR"}
{"id": "c1ce276296aa97e85eded6362e0ad2b80973bc92228513facedd911006df8937", "item_id": "4f9ab4a92b:21", "text": "来自 resultRGB 输出的 R 通道。"}
{"id": "2e12f103dc4a4b216b21cc6f017371b08507fc67f2a1ad9f133aa333afe0fc11", "item_id": "4f9ab4a92b:22", "text": "resultG"}
{"id": "009cc7a7eb8d7664fe8e8a024e817626113dd5198fc3a164f5ec297f2fa68da3", "item_id": "4f9ab4a92b:23", "text": "来自 resultRGB 输出的 G 通道。"}
{"id": "c3719f180d82ecafb70ce347c3499e7668a3d9262533cadae303c770922865ff", "item_id": "4f9ab4a92b:24", "text": "resultB"}
{"id": "d1e2217f59ea1bd29de7ec3ac2c05c763eca2c3bf612f3e04ff7cfd536f9f8e0", "item_id": "4f9ab4a92b:25", "text": "来自 resultRGB 输出的 B 通道。"}
